title: Modest Mouse - Sad Sappy Sucker
description:
Modest Mouse
Sad Sappy Sucker
1994

This is some of the earliest and possibly the best music made by now-famous Modest Mouse.  If you haven&#039;t heard this stuff but are a big fan, I really recommend it.  If you&#039;ve only heard "Float On" then you&#039;re going to hate this, so you might as well hit the &#039;Back&#039; button now.  

The first half of the album consists of full length, beautiful songs.  The quality is much worse than the newer Modest Mouse albums, but it adds to the trashy beauty of Isaac Brock&#039;s style.  The second half is composed of what sounds like Brock messing around in his bedroom, recording things sporadically.  

I love this album and here it is for all of you to share with me.
